But between this rod and that rod there is a vast difference; from
this action (magic) to that action (miracle) is a great way.

This action is followed by the curse of God; that action receives in
payment the mercy of God.

The infidels in contending (for equality with the prophets and saints)
have the nature of an ape： the evil nature is a canker within the
breast.
